overview: Girls aren't the only ones who want to have fun. Boys want the same thing! And no one wants it more than Especially Anton Marceau, Diego Martin, Timber Harvest, Billy Saint, Just Cross, Justin Stone, Payton Connor, Chris Summers, and Andrew Callahan. Yes, they like cuddling and a bit of romance and, eventually, they want to settle down. But before they find the one to have and to hold, all these twinks want to do is fuck bareback and sow some wild oats in To Have And To Hole.
title: To Have and to Hole
